## Notes
- **Raw Input API** — fallback if polling bermasalah dengan anti-cheat tertentu.
  Registrasi: `RegisterRawInputDevices(usUsage=0x01/mouse, RIDEV_INPUTSINK)`.
  Butuh hidden window (`HWND_MESSAGE`) + message pump + `WM_INPUT` handler.
  Referensi: https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/win32/inputdev/using-raw-input
